Recommends: ptouch-print
Description: GUI for the Brother PT-P710BT label printer
 A PyQt6 desktop GUI that wraps the ptouch-print CLI for the Brother
 P-Touch Cube (PT-P710BT) on Linux. Provides multi-line text entry,
 font/alignment controls, live tape preview, chain printing, image
 insertion, and one-click printing over USB.
